Dear MizzB I am 20-year-old woman in a relationship but my boyfriend&rsquo;s anger problem is starting to affect me. I have lost confidence in myself because of the things he says to me when he is angry. Please help me. - &nbsp;Lacking Confidence Dear Lacking ConfidenceAnger is a venomous emotion that can be fatal if not dealt with. All things considered, it is normal to lose confidence in yourself because of your situation. His behaviour will affect the way you see yourself and might set limitations on how far you can go in life. Talk to your boyfriend about getting help for his emotional problems.If he is unwilling to do so, then make the decision to save yourself. You have the power to free yourself and he has the choice to seek help for the management of his anger.